title: Ten Thousand Reward (1927 silent film) directed by Alan Hale, Sr.

sources.title: Ten Thousand Reward (1927 silent film) directed by Alan Hale, Sr.
sources.description:
A nation on wheels! If you drive a car don't miss this one!
Bankrupt in New York? California, here we come! That, in a nutshell, is the plot of Rubber Tires / Ten Thousand Reward.  A romantic road comedy from the tail end of the silent era.  Along the way, they encounter old flames, relentless pursuers, and unexpected twists in their quest to reclaim their valuable car.

Original title: Rubber Tires (1927) AKA: Ten Thousand Reward

Black & White version: https://youtu.be/ZrBb5gNHzB0


Director: Alan Hale
Writer: Frank Condon, Tay Garnett, Zelda Sears
Stars: Bessie Love, Erwin Connelly, Frank Coghlan Jr.
Genres: Colorized classics, Adventure, Comedy, Silent film


@CultCinemaClassics
